->  present in JAVA.LANG.STRINGBUILDER


->    String builders support mutable strings and threads are not Present.
      Instances of StringBuilder are not safe for use by multiple threads.
      
      
->  In String Builder Objects can be created only using NEW keyword.

->  Stringbuilder class impliments Serializable, Appendable<String>, Charsequence interface.

->  Stringbuilder class is final and it can't be inherited.

->  Stringbuilder class is immediate sub-class of object class.
    
->  StringBuilder is like a String but canbe modified without creating any de refrenced objects.

->  Here we cannot perform Concatination operation means, We can use "+" operator to perform 
    addition operation, else we can use append keyword.
    
->  Any modifications to StringBuffer canbe done only by using the methods of StringBuffer class.

->  toString() of Object class is OVERRIDDEN in Stringbuilder class which returns an
    String value present in given String.
    But Hashcode method and equals methods are can't be Overridden in StringBuilder Class.
